0. As a daily user of the website, I want to be able to post any post, be it a picture of an art piece
I made.
1. for the front end we used vanilla HTML, CSS, and JS
for the backend, we used flask to connect the front end to the backend
for the database, we used SQLite (the database was written in SQL)
